<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="30" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="30">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="30">
The record of this species by 
<bibRefCitation author="Fuentes, F" journalOrPublisher="Boletin del Museo Nacional de Chile" pageId="16" pageNumber="43" pagination="285 - 318" title="Contribucion al estudio de la fauna de la Isla de Pascua." volume="7" year="1914">Fuentes (1914)</bibRefCitation>
needs to be confirmed since this littoral species has often been confused with other species in the past. Unfortunately, no specimens of 
<taxonomicName class="Malacostraca" family="Ligiidae" genus="Ligia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ligia" order="Isopoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="30" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Ligia</taxonomicName>
have been recently collected from Rapa Nui, most likely due to lack of investigations along the littoral zones of the island.
</paragraph>
